  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Petit Tournalin is well known for its food. For breakfast you can tuck into a delicious buffet with hot choices as well as homemade cakes and jams.</p>
<p>Dinner is in the hotel's charming restaurant with chalet-style décor and lovely mountain views. You can enjoy a four-course meal with a choice. If you're a wine lover then there's an excellent selection available (payable locally).</p>
<p>Packed lunches are also available for approx. €10. They include a sandwich, a snack, fruit and water.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
