  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Petit Tournalin is a cosy, family-run hotel with welcoming staff and enviable views across the mountains. If you're looking to take on the walking trails, the Petit Tournalin is the perfect base in the mountains to relax after a day of hiking.</p>
<h2>A mountain retreat</h2>
<p>You're around 500 metres away from the village which means you can enjoy the peace and tranquillity of the mountains but you're within walking distance of the local amenities and lifts. Why not head to the lovely lounge and bar area after a day of hiking and enjoy an aperitivo - there is even a sauna and whirlpool if you truly want to relax. </p>
<h2>Enjoy delicious cuisine</h2>
<p>You're always well-fed at the Hotel Petit Tournalin with excellent food on offer. The restaurant with its cosy, chalet-style interior is an inviting experience coupled with delicious food and a great selection of wine (wine payable locally).</p>
<p><strong>Transfer time:</strong> approx. 2 hours by coach from Milan airport. </p>]]></description>
