  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Twin Rooms</strong> sleep up to two people and are located on the second floor of the hotel. These rooms have a balcony with mountain views.</p>
<p><strong>Comfort Rooms and Junior Suites</strong> are available on request, for a supplement, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Balcony</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Tea &amp; coffee making facilities are available on a request</li>
<li>Shower</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Minibar</li>
<li>Safe</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
